            "+@type": "Alternative title",
            "+@lang": "JA"
        },
        {
            "+content": "romance",
            "+@gid": "3802435295",
            "+@type": "Genres"
        },
        {
            "+content": "A high school boy, Itsuki Tomonari, becomes involved in a kidnapping and ends up caring for Hinako Konohana, a young lady from one of Japan's largest conglomerates. On the surface, Hinako seems to be a brilliant and charming girl, but in reality, she is a lazy girl with no life skills. However, due to family reasons, Hinako has to play the role of the \"perfect young lady\" at school. Wanting to protect her, Itsuki takes care of her very well. Eventually, Hinako begins to fawn on Itsuki with all her might… \"Now…if Itsuki isn't around, I would hate it.\" <em class=de-emphasized>(from manga)</em>",
            "+@type": "Plot Summary"
        },
